1
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:34,040
By day, parading through town with a courtesan,

2
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:35,120
getting ambushed by assassins.

3
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,359
By night,

4
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,040
a ruined hut outside the city,

5
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,480
and a ruckus at the Chancellor's manor.

6
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,760
There are only twelve hours in a day.

7
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,680
Is that even enough for you?

8
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:46,480
How does he know all this?

9
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,920
Did he plant a tracker on me?

10
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,959
Your Majesty, the Left Chancellor, he...

11
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:52,640
Enough.

12
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:53,879
Ning Chen.

13
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,439
As a Silver-robed Inspector,

14
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,400
acting so recklessly,

15
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,480
where is your sense of propriety?

16
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:00,920
Your Majesty, please calm your anger.

17
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,480
This subject acknowledges his fault.

18
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,120
Rise.

19
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,599
Thank you, Your Majesty.

20
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:17,199
The three thousand muskets have been assembled.

21
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:19,639
I've prepared one thousand soldiers for you.

22
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,400
In three days,

23
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,080
lead them to the frontier.

24
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:25,120
The frontier army has always been hostile to outsiders.

25
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,520
These one thousand soldiers

26
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:29,120
were handpicked by Old General Chen for you,

27
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,439
and are already familiar with operating muskets.

28
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,520
They can serve as your personal guards.

29
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,400
As for how to use them,

30
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,719
that's up to you.

31
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:39,520
Your Majesty, three thousand muskets

32
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:41,159
should be matched with three thousand soldiers, no?

33
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:42,479
One thousand is all I can give.

34
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,439
The rest,

35
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,719
I have other uses for them.

36
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,159
Taking a cut, huh?

37
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,199
Shipeng.

38
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:49,840
Here.

39
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,439
Bring the sword.

40
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,560
I bestow upon you the Imperial Sword.

41
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:01,080
To see this sword is to see me in person.

42
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:04,599
Do not disappoint me or the old general.

43
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,560
Your Majesty, a real sword!

44
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,080
What... what did you say?

45
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,560
What I meant was,

46
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,000
so this is the Imperial Sword.

47
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,439
It's my first time seeing one.

48
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,599
Wielding the Imperial Sword

49
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:23,159
grants the right to execute first, report later,

50
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:25,039
but you must never abuse it for personal vendettas.

51
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:27,840
Tomorrow I shall issue a decree

52
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,080
naming you Great General of the Northern Expedition.

53
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,520
Thank you, Your Majesty.

54
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,680
I recall that your mother

55
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,960
hailed from Yang'an County, Lingzhou.

56
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:43,199
Yesterday I received a report

57
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,520
that bandits are rampant there.

58
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,080
The county garrison lacks the strength to handle it.

59
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,759
On your way to the frontier,

60
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,280
sailing downstream,

61
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:51,560
you'll pass right through Lingzhou.

62
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,280
The old man's digging into my family records.

63
00:03:55,919 --> 00:03:58,120
So this bandit problem,

64
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,879
I'll leave it to you.

65
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,360
This subject accepts the decree.

66
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,039
Now scram.

67
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,080
Hold on.

68
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,960
Do you know how

69
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,400
to make a kite?

70
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,920
Honestly, Imperial Father.

71
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,120
I know how to make a kite.

72
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,240
Why does Ning Chen have to help me?

73
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,759
Greetings, Princess Huai'an.

74
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,399
Somehow it feels like

75
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,279
he's gotten quite a bit more handsome

76
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,639
since the last time I saw him.

77
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:44,720
Princess.

78
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,240
Princess.

79
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,079
That Ning Chen,

80
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,439
I know how to make kites.

81
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,319
Why did Imperial Father send you to help me?

82
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,879
You can make kites?

83
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,120
Of course.

84
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,240
I learned from the palace masters.

85
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,879
My kites are definitely better than yours.

86
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,199
What is His Majesty up to?

87
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,800
Could it be...

88
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,800
he wants to pair me with the Princess?

89
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:09,959
Forget it.

90
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,959
Since Imperial Father sent you,

91
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,160
that means

92
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,959
your kites must be pretty good too.

93
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,720
How about this?

94
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,160
Let's have a contest.

95
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,680
See whose kite is prettier.

96
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,160
If you win,

97
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,720
I'll reward you with a hundred taels of gold.

98
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,920
If you lose,

99
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,120
then you'll write me a poem.

100
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,120
It's settled then.

101
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,079
As the Princess wishes.

102
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:31,959
Good.

103
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,399
You lost.

104
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:18,399
Ning Chen,

105
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,759
a bet's a bet.

106
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,399
Write me a poem.

107
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,759
Name the topic, Princess.

108
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,920
I haven't seen snow in so long.

109
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,319
So how about this?

110
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,519
Snow shall be the theme.

111
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,959
If you can't think of anything,

112
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,639
I can give you a few days.

113
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:35,439
Take your time.

114
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:35,920
No need.

115
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:36,879
I've already got one.

116
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,120
Then hurry and say it.

117
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,600
Listen carefully, Princess.

118
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:46,360
One flake, one flake, and another flake,

119
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,639
two flakes, three flakes, four, five flakes.

120
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,000
How dare you, Ning Chen!

121
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,959
Are you mocking me?

122
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,680
Don't be hasty, Princess.

123
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:58,920
I'm not finished yet.

124
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,040
Were you about to say,

125
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,399
"five flakes, six flakes, seven, eight flakes"?

126
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,480
The Princess is truly six, indeed.

127
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,279
How dare you!

128
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,120
You dare call me a six-year-old?

129
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,920
You're dead. Just you wait!

130
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,360
Lord Ning, you'd better run.

131
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,120
Why?

132
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,079
Princess!

133
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,120
Stop it, Ning Chen!

134
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:20,800
Get away.

135
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:21,519
Get out of my way!

136
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,759
Ning Chen, you're dead today!

137
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,040
Princess, I'll beat you to death!

138
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,439
Princess, be careful!

139
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,439
Ning Chen, I...

140
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,240
Watch out, Princess!

141
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:28,959
Stop right there!

142
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,240
Stop, Princess!

143
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,720
Today I'll beat you to death!

144
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,480
Put down the feather duster first.

145
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,279
I won't! Why should I?

146
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:39,279
If you're this fierce, no one will marry you.

147
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,519
You dare call me fierce?

148
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,000
If no one will marry me, I'll marry you.

149
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,959
And I'll, I'll beat you every single day.

150
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:52,399
That's just cruel!

151
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,279
You'd marry me

152
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:56,480
just to be that vicious?

153
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,759
I never want to see you again!

154
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:04,519
Huai'an.

155
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:04,839
Huai'an!

156
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:05,639
You get out of my sight too!

157
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,639
I'll handle this for you.

158
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,639
Ning Chen.

159
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:13,959
Greetings, Your Majesty.

160
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,920
Is my daughter so unworthy?

161
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:19,079
Her Highness is breathtakingly beautiful,

162
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:20,160
and exceptionally talented.

163
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:22,240
Beauty and wisdom combined.

164
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:23,879
No one can compare to her.

165
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,360
Then why did you say

166
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,920
no one would want her?

167
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:28,839
I was just joking with the Princess.

168
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,800
I didn't mean it at all.

169
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:30,839
Right, Princess?

170
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,519
Not funny.

171
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,600
The Princess wants to marry you.

172
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,399
And you feel wronged by that?

173
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,200
Not wronged.

174
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,639
It's just that I am nobody.

175
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,320
Untalented in letters or arms.

176
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:46,399
How could I dare aspire to the Princess?

177
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,639
Wouldn't that ruin her future?

178
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,960
Only a fool would marry a princess.

179
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,000
Can't even take concubines.

180
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,279
What would become of Yu Die?

181
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,720
You despise my daughter that much?

182
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,600
Even debasing yourself to avoid her?

183
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:02,639
Not at all, Your Maj-

184
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,480
Shut up.

185
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,919
How dare you, Ning Chen!

186
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,000
Insulting the Princess, offending the royal family!

187
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,639
Drag him out!

188
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:08,919
Thirty strokes of the rod!

189
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:09,480
Go!

190
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,360
Wait a moment.

191
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:11,840
Your Majesty.

192
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,600
I depart for battle in a few days.

193
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,000
If I'm beaten and injured here,

194
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,759
won't that delay my journey?

195
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,399
No matter.

196
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,159
I've calculated it all for you.

197
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,399
You set sail the day after tomorrow.

198
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,679
Going downstream,

199
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:25,879
to reach Lingzhou

200
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,960
will take about five days.

201
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,720
Plus today and tomorrow,

202
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,120
that's seven days total.

203
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:32,440
By the time you arrive,

204
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,519
your wounds will have healed.

205
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,360
Off you go.

206
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:38,639
Your Majesty!

207
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:39,639
Your Majesty, please don't do this!

208
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:40,120
I...

209
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:40,840
Wait, all of you!

210
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,000
Let go of him, all of you!

211
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:45,799
Imperial Father.

212
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,440
I was just teasing Ning Chen earlier.

213
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,720
He didn't insult me.

214
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,320
Imperial Father, please don't beat him.

215
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,200
He came to help me make a kite,

216
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,120
and now he gets a beating?

217
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,480
That's just cruel, Imperial Father!

218
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,240
The Princess may be a bit spoiled,

219
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:02,000
but her heart is truly kind.

220
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:09,000
Huai'an even pleaded for you.

221
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:09,759
Aren't you...

222
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:11,399
Aren't you going to say something?

223
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:15,200
Your Highness is as kind as you are beautiful.

224
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:18,000
Loved by all, adored by everyone.

225
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,360
Such a smooth talker.

226
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,159
I think you deserve a flogging.

227
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:25,159
This lad clearly has a silver tongue,

228
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,639
so why can't he take a hint?

229
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,759
Enough.

230
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,960
Since Huai'an has pleaded for you,

231
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,840
I shall spare you for now.

232
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:33,879
However,

233
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:35,919
if you upset Huai'an again,

234
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:36,519
then...

235
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,519
then you must cheer her up for me.

236
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:41,480
That poem you just recited,

237
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:42,919
it was rather poorly written.

238
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,120
As punishment, write another.

239
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,039
If it's bad again,

240
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,279
you'll go straight to receive your flogging.

241
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:49,120
Wind and snow pressed me down for years,

242
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,320
yet I laugh, they're light as cotton.

243
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:56,480
They say the capital blooms like brocade,

244
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:00,759
but spring eluded me upon arrival.

245
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,679
Using imagery to speak of himself.

246
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:05,279
He's voicing the bitterness in his heart.

247
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,240
Brother Crown Prince once told me

248
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:10,519
Ning Chen had a hard life in the Ning family.

249
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,039
A fine poem.

250
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,559
Though the mood is a bit heavy.

251
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,600
So have I passed?

252
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:19,840
You've passed.

253
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:21,399
You've passed.

254
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,879
You do have a bit of talent.

255
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,240
My Huai'an loves poetry,

256
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:28,240
and she's about your age.

257
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,639
So I shall permit you,

258
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,039
upon returning from the campaign,

259
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:33,559
to visit Huai'an in the palace anytime.

260
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,799
You're really making things difficult for me.

261
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:39,600
Got nothing to do? Go handle state affairs!

262
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,679
Stop with the reckless matchmaking, please.

263
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,639
Why is my stomach growling?

264
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,639
I'm hungry too.

265
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,200
Has my lunch arrived?

266
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,159
Yes, Your Majesty.

267
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:54,080
Then the three of us shall dine together.

268
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:54,879
Your Majesty,

269
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:56,240
the Inspectorate has much work to do.

270
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,000
This subject won't...

271
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:57,600
You...

272
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:00,519
Are you a killjoy?

273
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:01,159
Exactly.

274
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:01,639
You...

275
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:02,159
Get out!

276
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,120
Out, out, out!

277
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:17,960
I take my leave.

278
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,320
Imperial Father!

279
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,639
You just let him go like that?

280
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,480
I didn't actually mean for him to leave.

281
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:27,399
But he really did walk right out!

282
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,440
I'm so furious!
